column5:
Merge pull request #661 from drsassafras/master

Removed BOM encoding and applied Lossless image compression

Core: Prevent JS error when panel doesn't exist. Fixes #659

With showMultiple: 2 & an odd number of slides, the sixth slide
doesn't exist; the last slide is now used in calculating the
"expected" dimension
Video: Use https for YouTub api calls. Fixes #648
Demos: Use https for external files. Fixes #646
Video: force vimeo iframe to use https. Fixes #645

Merge pull request #604 from christian-seifert/master

Updateable anythingSliderVideo

Merge pull request #584 from npn66nicke/master

Added config and logic (and demos) for aspectRatio (scale parameter).
aspectRatio: fixed formatting replaced expanded tabs (spaces) with real TABs
Added config and logic (and demos) for aspectRatio (scale parameter).
added component.json for bower registration. Fixes #566.
fade mode now sets panel visibility when resumeOnVisible is true. Fixes #559.
css should now pass css3 validation. Fixes #556
fixed video extension to properly work across multiple sliders; see #548
added onVideoInitialized callback to video extension

Merge pull request #542 from wearetelescopic/master

Added callback for the resize event

Update jquery.anythingslider.js

Added new callback for slider resize: onSliderResize
stopAtEnd and showMultiple no longer shows empty panels - fixes #515
video extension now uses YouTube iframe api script - should fix #191, #263, #333, #454, #501 and #525
platRtl is now only applied to the slideshow; see #526
HTML5 video behaves properly when resumeOnVisible is set; see #525
vertical mode now works with showMultiple

Merge pull request #485 from mlms13/master

Prevent embedded Youtube videos from breaking in iOS
Only use swfobject if the browser supports Flash
bump version again, removing the "v" in the tag
removed clearing height on outer wrapper for expand option. Fixes #476
completely ignore hash when hashTags is false
updated z-index in all themes; fixes #447
slideshow now stops when page isn't visible
overall width will now update properly, fixes issue #459
fixed all links to css-tricks; fixed fx thumbnail demo

Add anchors for easier external linking

Add anchors for easier external linking
Example: http://proloser.github.com/AnythingSlider/#default-options
demo only: captions css fixed to position absolute
remove opacity & set z-index in css. Fix for #379
modified fade mode to optionally hide panels
fix IE9 flashing before fade - issue #377
allow setting animation time to zero via method
fixed error when buildArrows is false and stopAtEnd is true. Fixes #343.
Don't add anythingControls when empty. Fixes #342.
doing my part to eradicate the bubble monster
updated playground link - added ul#slider to override default css
fixed id in hash not working
disabled class now applied to arrows external to slider
disable forms & remove name attribute in cloned slides
current tab now updates before animation
tooltips class & title now applied properly
id hash + non-infinite slides, now chooses correct slide
Fix for issue #264 - do not animate, if same size
added json package for jquery plugin repository
silly trailing comma breaking every version of IE in existence
moved resume video option to plugin core
fixed clicking links in multiple slides
fixed no callbacks when animationTime was zero

Fixed typo appendFowardTo->appendForwardTo
fixed clicking links in multiple slides
removed theme directory option & unordered list restriction
single slide bug fix & option variable
